Package: leedstrams
Title: Tools for Working with Leeds Historic Tram Map Tiles
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
    person("ITS", "Leeds", role = c("cph")),
    person("Robin", "Lovelace", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "robin@example.com")
  )
Author: ITS Leeds [cph], Robin Lovelace [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Robin Lovelace <robin@example.com>
Description: Helper functions to work with National Library of Scotland (NLS)
    OS town plan tile pyramids, including XYZ tile maths, downloading, and
    creating stitched mosaics with 'terra'.
